## Application Objective

- This app is a news feed crawler that retrieve data from news site like https://www.theverge.com/, https://techcrunch.com/, https://www.blognone.com/, https://news.ycombinator.com/, to shows all of them in a page.
- it should support multiple sites crawling
- it should be able to retrieve new news every hour
- it should store or cache the retrieved data as JSON in sources/<site-name>/<date> for showing on frontend
- it should be able to crawl through pagination of sites

It is a mobile friendly application